{"tid":364592,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"單靠少少既資料，有冇可能會搵到我爸爸","createTime":"2017-08-18T13:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T13:28:53.000Z","uid":137741,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32c263921659cabc206dad3d70de63914fefaa7b","tid":364592,"uid":137741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T13:56:06.000Z","msg":"依件事我一直都唔敢同現實既朋友講，因為覺得唔好意思<br />\n我又請唔起尋人專家，所以好想問一下，到底有冇方法搵返我爸爸<br />\n<br />\n當年我媽媽算係好玩得既女仔，成日都去飲酒<br />\n結果就同一個外國男人一夜情，後尾生左我出黎<br />\n依件事都係近幾年媽媽身體變差先同我講<br />\n以前我一直都以為爸爸只係意外好早就過左身<br />\n<br />\n依家有既資料，就大概只有佢既名(姓都冇)、以前係邊返工同埋佢係波蘭人<br />\n而且唔肯定到底係唔係真<br />\n就算係真，可以點樣搵<br />\n就算搵到，又點可以無啦啦話佢多左個女<br />\n當然我唔會影響到人地生活，但最起碼我想知爸爸係邊個<br />\n<br />\n如果只係有依D資料，你地覺得搵到佢既機會大唔大? 我會靠自己去搵"},{"pid":"e20328b80afa4bb1885a1b1b6feab28a810b854e","tid":364592,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T13:58:29.000Z","msg":"歐洲妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c269aeb188c13e77d8bc253470a81f139031c47d","tid":364592,"uid":137741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:03:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歐洲妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2f06c203c12a83d349bc4a2f83d090a451a714","tid":364592,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:05:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>歐洲妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁個樣有冇分別?"},{"pid":"6dea6df6c7f15c6e00e15d16562f3d402ba60d1e","tid":364592,"uid":78018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:06:30.000Z","msg":"mixed？"},{"pid":"6703ff5ad844bc7525c18de612a1406dd83080e9","tid":364592,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:07:40.000Z","msg":"同你一齊搵啦"},{"pid":"bc5046eefe8ef0345adbb20b2450f64808289e60","tid":364592,"uid":137741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:13:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>歐洲妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁個樣有冇分別?</blockquote><br />\n<em>Homo sapiens</em><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n認真，我想搵好耐<br />\n但另一個矛盾係我媽媽唔知道我想搵佢<br />\n我亦唔敢同佢講我想搵佢<br />\n因為我諗我媽媽都太辛苦啦"},{"pid":"bdf6f2040a5edc3b8309ac88b9f37a349f77acaf","tid":364592,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:48:33.000Z","msg":"其實真係好大海撈針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都幫推"},{"pid":"79fd262225d816fa47c2ed24eea11f4ded8ddf35","tid":364592,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:52:10.000Z","msg":"有心既用時間同錢應該搵到"},{"pid":"459109ae992278751894fba8b39dab2dede800b1","tid":364592,"uid":124277,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:53:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有心既用時間同錢應該搵到</blockquote><br />\nwow你係點唸到架"},{"pid":"46e44fef692df85465188835d7c28572c172ab64","tid":364592,"uid":136568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:59:14.000Z","msg":"絲打不妨講低邊間公司做過話唔定有人知呢"},{"pid":"30d999c81f4c7b985a1b698e80a65fec30b6202f","tid":364592,"uid":137741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T15:04:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實真係好大海撈針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都幫推</blockquote><br />\n唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055e8a8f020237917d16b5142a4c483108d6d929","tid":364592,"uid":137741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有心既用時間同錢應該搵到</blockquote><br />\nwow你係點唸到架</blockquote><br />\n錢就真係冇...屋企本身負擔已經重，不可能咁樣哂錢"},{"pid":"6d7a08e7b13c081a062c294fbba2a715850fd40d","tid":364592,"uid":137741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T15:08:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打不妨講低邊間公司做過話唔定有人知呢</blockquote><br />\n佢應該係華沙理工大學度教書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我媽媽唔肯定，因為冇可能記得全名，但佢印象中係理工學院黎<br />\n而我CHECK過可能係依間，因為媽媽話過佢係華沙返工"},{"pid":"827ea48fda9a2b9c50e87a5405bdde6025611452","tid":364592,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T15:11:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>絲打不妨講低邊間公司做過話唔定有人知呢</blockquote><br />\n佢應該係華沙理工大學度教書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我媽媽唔肯定，因為冇可能記得全名，但佢印象中係理工學院黎<br />\n而我CHECK過可能係依間，因為媽媽話過佢係華沙返工</blockquote><br />\nFacebook有冇佢名?"},{"pid":"eb91ad23d8986a8a62e92a1803ef99ff10be848a","tid":364592,"uid":137741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T15:16:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>絲打不妨講低邊間公司做過話唔定有人知呢</blockquote><br />\n佢應該係華沙理工大學度教書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我媽媽唔肯定，因為冇可能記得全名，但佢印象中係理工學院黎<br />\n而我CHECK過可能係依間，因為媽媽話過佢係華沙返工</blockquote><br />\nFacebook有冇佢名?</blockquote><br />\n因為只係得名，所以好難好難好難搵<br />\n正如係facebook搵Tom, Ken咁"},{"pid":"d667818f94bdb3169964e79c319d3eb818c0e50c","tid":364592,"uid":76105,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T15:30:55.000Z","msg":"搵我老豆做咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我唔想有兄弟姊妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a4c4fc9852bcd798bdf16c7f89ca595527f310","tid":364592,"uid":75137,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:32:51.000Z","msg":"&quot;好玩得&quot;? <br />\n<br />\n咪即係公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac23cf358c5873c305c9f4dc45a6de4327